data.name: label3.Text
data.value: In the modern day, there's no reason a DJ shouldn't accept requests from their listeners. This plugin will organize your requests for you in a neat fashion, allowing you to be a more efficient dj. Keep on spinning those records!

data.name: HCRT.ToolTipText
data.value:
When turned OFF, all channel requests will be rewritten. These requests will also go to the request console.
When turned ON, you will see the raw !request commands in your IRC logs. Requests will still go to the request console.

data.name: HPRT.ToolTipText
data.value:
When turned OFF, all private requests will be hidden. These requests will go to the request console.
When turned ON, you will see the raw !request commands in your IRC logs. Requests will still go to the request console.
